title: Saying Minnesota has 'been through a lot,' Klobuchar announces bid for governor
description: Democratic Sen. Amy Klobuchar announced her run for Minnesota governor early Thursday. There is already a crowded field of Republicans in a race where immigration enforcement has become a key issue.
